Scrapyਞᤰ
Scrapyጱਞᤰํग़ᐿොୗ҅ਙඪ೮Python2.7ᇇ๜݊զӤ౲Python3.3ᇇ๜݊զӤ̶ӥᶎ᧔กPython3
ሾहӥጱਞᤰᬦᑕ̶
Scrapyׁᩢጱପྲ᫾ग़҅ᛗ੝ᵱᥝׁᩢପํTwisted 14.0҅lxml 3.4҅pyOpenSSL 0.14̶ᘒࣁӧݶଘ
ݣሾह݈ݱӧፘݶ҅ಅզࣁਞᤰԏڹ๋অᏟכ಩ӞԶच๜ପਞᤰঅ҅੦ٌฎWindows̶
Anaconda
ᬯᐿොဩฎӞᐿྲ᫾ᓌܔጱਞᤰScrapyጱොဩҁ੦ٌฎ੒Windows๶᧔҂֦҅ݢզֵአᧆොဩਞᤰ҅
Ԟݢզᭌአӥ෈Ӿӫአଘݣጱਞᤰොဩ̶
Anacondaฎ۱ތԧଉአጱහഝᑀ਍ପጱPythonݎᤈᇇ๜҅ইຎဌํਞᤰ҅ݢզ
کhttps://www.continuum.io/downloadsӥ᫹੒ଫଘݣጱ۱ਞᤰ̶
ইຎ૪ᕪਞᤰ҅ᮎԍݢզ᫷ຂࣈ᭗ᬦ conda ޸եਞᤰScrapy̶
ਞᤰ޸եইӥғ
conda install Scrapy
Windows
ਞᤰlxml
๋অጱਞᤰොୗฎ᭗ᬦwheel෈կ๶ਞᤰ҅http://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/҅՗ᧆᗑᒊತ
کlxmlጱፘى෈կ̶؃ইฎPython3.5ᇇ๜҅WIndows 64֖ᔮᕹ҅ᮎ੪ತک
lxml‑3.7.2‑cp35‑cp35m‑win_amd64.whl ᬯӻ෈կଚӥ᫹҅ᆐݸ᭗ᬦpipਞᤰ̶
ӥ᫹ԏݸ҅ᬩᤈইӥ޸եਞᤰғ
pip3 install wheel
pip3 install lxml‑3.7.2‑cp35‑cp35m‑win_amd64.whl
ݢܨਠ౮lxmlጱਞᤰٌ҅՜෈կ๊ഘ෈կݢܨݷ̶
ਞᤰpyOpenSSL
ਥොᗑᒊӥ᫹wheel෈կ҅https://pypi.python.org/pypi/pyOpenSSL#downloads҅ই୮ڹ๋ෛᇇ๜
ݷᑍฎpyOpenSSL-16.2.0-py2.py3-none-any.whl҅ӥ᫹ݸਞᤰݢܨ̶
pip3 install pyOpenSSL-16.2.0-py2.py3-none-any.whl
ਞᤰTwisted
ݶቘ҅http://www.lfd.uci.edu/~gohlke/pythonlibs/#twistedӥ᫹wheel෈կ҅ڥአpipਞᤰݢܨ̶
ইPython 3.5ᇇ๜҅Windows 64֖ᔮᕹ҅ӥ᫹ Twisted‑17.1.0‑cp35‑cp35m‑win_amd64.whl҅ᆐݸ
pipਞᤰ̶
pip3 install Twisted‑17.1.0‑cp35‑cp35m‑win_amd64.whl
ਞᤰpywin32
՗ਥොᗑᒊ https://sourceforge.net/projects/pywin32/files/pywin32/Build%20220/ ӥ᫹੒ଫᇇ๜
̶ݢܨጱਞᤰ۱ਞᤰ
ਞᤰScrapy
๋ݸਞᤰScrapyݢܨׁ҅ᆐֵአpip҅޸եইӥғ
pip3 install Scrapy
CentOS̵RedHat̵Fedora
ׁᩢପਞᤰ
ᏟכӞԶ஠ᶳጱᔄପ૪ᕪਞᤰ҅ᬩᤈইӥ޸եғ
sudo yum groupinstall development tools
sudo yum install python34-devel epel-release libxslt-devel libxml2-devel openssldevel
ਞᤰScrapy
եғ޸ᬩᤈইӥ҅ݢܨአpipਞᤰScrapyڥ
pip3 install Scrapy
Ubuntu̵Debian̵Deepin
ׁᩢପਞᤰ
ḒضᏟכӞԶ஠ᶳጱᔄପ૪ᕪਞᤰ҅ᬩᤈইӥ޸եғ
sudo apt-get install build-essential python3-dev libssl-dev libffi-dev libxml2
libxml2-dev libxslt1-dev zlib1g-dev
ਞᤰScrapy
եғ޸ᬩᤈইӥ҅ݢܨአpipਞᤰScrapyڥ
pip3 install Scrapy
Mac OS
ׁᩢପਞᤰ
ࣁMacӤ຅ୌScrapyጱׁᩢପᵱᥝCᖫᦲ࢏զ݊୏ݎ१෈կ҅ਙӞᛱኧXcode൉׀҅ᬩᤈইӥ޸եਞᤰ
ғݢܨ
xcode-select --install
ਞᤰScrapy
եғ޸ᬩᤈইӥ҅ݢܨአpipਞᤰScrapyڥ
pip3 install Scrapy
ḵᦤ
ਞᤰԏݸ҅޸ࣁեᤈӥᬌف scrapy ҅ইຎڊሿᔄ֒ӥොጱᕮຎ҅੪ᦤกScrapyਞᤰ౮ۑ̶
ଉᥠᲙ᧏
pkg_resources.VersionConflict: (six 1.5.2 (/usr/lib/python3/dist-packages),
Requirement.parse('six>=1.6.0'))
six۱ᇇ๜ᬦ֗҅six۱ฎӞӻ൉׀਻ّPython2޾Python3ጱପ҅܋ᕆsix۱ݢܨ̶
sudo pip3 install -U six
c/_cffi_backend.c:15:17: fatal error: ffi.h: No such file or directory
ᗌ੝Libffiᬯӻପ̶ՋԍฎlibffiҘ“FFI” ጱݷقฎ Foreign Function Interface҅᭗ଉ೰ጱฎ꧋ᦜզӞᐿ
᧍᥺ᖫٟጱդᎱ᧣አݚӞᐿ᧍᥺ጱդᎱ̶ᘒLibffiପݝ൉׀๋ԧବ੶ጱ̵Өຝ຅ፘىጱ̵ਠෆጱ”FFI”̶
̶ݢܨਞᤰፘଫጱପ
Ubuntu̵Debianғ
sudo apt-get install build-essential libssl-dev libffi-dev python3-dev
CentOS̵RedHat:
sudo yum install gcc libffi-devel python-devel openssl-devel
ImportError: No module named 'cryptography'
̶ݢܨአpipਞᤰڥ҅ᕟկىጱፘੂے੝ᬯฎᗌ
sudo pip3 install cryptography
ImportError: No module named 'packaging'
ᗌ੝packagingᬯӻ۱҅ਙ൉׀ԧPython۱ጱ໐ஞۑᚆ҅ڥአpipਞᤰݢܨ̶
sudo pip3 install packaging
ImportError: No module named 'appdirs'
ᗌ੝appdirsᬯӻ۱҅ਙአ๶Ꮯਧ෈կፓ୯҅ڥአpipܔᇿਞᤰݢܨ̶
sudo pip3 install appdirs